name: American Failure Roundel
description: ROUNDEL We wanted something that supported our satirics, yet was obviously serious. The USAF (United States American Failure) Roundel came to be. The first two shirts released are our precursors. Our shirts are in limited supply due to the idea that no one likes seeing someone wearing what you are and because we're cheap and didn't have enough to buy more. But we came up with the idea a small amount, with a variety of different shirt colors. When this shirt color runs out, you may not see it for a while, but you might see the design recycled. Our shirts can't make you feel better about yourself. There aren't any anorexic models hired to wear our shirts. We are conflict orientated, but not meant to be controversial. Only trying to force the real problems into everyday life. Just like a company selling a product, telling you what you need to have in your life. We're doing the same. Our shirts are 'made in Downtown LA'. The price ($17) includes tax, COGS, profit. Shipping EVERYWHERE in the US is $3.00. Outside US, ..USD isn't doing well so it's $8.00.
